    • confirmCart_func

      public void confirmCart_func(SpinnerModel[] cart_spinner, SpinnerModel[] cart_spinner_menu, JTextArea display_box, String[] items, String[] menu_items, double[] menu_prices, double order_total_price, JTextArea comment_textarea, JLabel total_price_label)
      This function executes an order and updates database with items in the shopping cart
      Parameters:
      cart_spinner - Spinner that contains the inventory items to be displayed
      cart_spinner_menu - Spinner that contains the menu items to be desiplayed
      display_box - JTextArea object that will hold the text to be displayed
      items - An array of all the inventory items
      menu_items - An array of all the menu items
      menu_prices - An array of the price of menu items
      order_total_price - Holds the total price of all items in the cart
      comment_textarea - Holds the name of the items selected
      total_price_label - A label that contains that price of all items ordered
